Job Description:
EDUCATION & REQUIREMENTS:
Education Level required: Master’s degree in computer science, social science, mathematics, statistics or engineering. Additional years of experience can be considered with Bachelor’s degree.

Relevant experience required: Minimum of 8 years’ extensive experience in a related field.
Knowledge required: Strong proficiency with developing web and mobile applications, Visual Studio 2015+, Microsoft SQL Server 2016+, C#, ASP.Net, Java, Python, PHP, JavaScript (JQuery Angular), HTML 5, Mobile IOS and Android application development platforms, Microsoft Office applications and Microsoft Operating Systems. Experience with Application API’s (REST, SOAP, Oauth); Experience with Crystal Reports 11.x, Power BI, and Tableau are a plus; Ability to work with a diverse group of people at both a functional and technical level and communicate at a level appropriate to audience;
Ability to work both independently and as part of a team;
Strong written and verbal communication skills.
